about_the_job:
Servicology is an international company that evolves by supporting our customers’ products. We love good products. Such products, marketing, and communication of which go straight to the heart. Products that love their customers and help them become more successful.

Currently, we are looking for an Affiliate Marketing Manager!

Your main tasks at the position will be to:
Work with current partners in the region on establishing digital affiliate marketing campaigns;
Search for new partners in the region;
Provide support for partners, collect feedback, and offer new mechanics of promotions for their development.

Requirements:
Experience in affiliate programs/affiliate marketing;
Experience in influencer marketing;
Knowledge of English (upper-intermediate level and above);
Knowledge of Bahasa Indonesia (advanced level and above);
Customer-focused approach;
Experience with online projects in the financial sector will be an advantage;
Ability to collect, analyze and visualize information in Excel and PowerPoint.

Conditions:
28 days of paid vacation annually + unlimited paid days off.
An unlimited number of paid sick leave days.
Online work demands a good Internet connection. We will compensate you for the Internet—25$ per month.
We have a Happy Employee Fund. Every month, Servicology allocates a budget so that we can all get our endorphins going together. We can take part in online games, quizzes, and any other activities to have fun and get to know each other better.
And so much more!
